high_descs: Go around the sidetable ahead to exit the room through the left, then right right and go through the doorway, heading for the bedstand.
Pick up the grape from the bedstand.
Turn around and head through the doorway, straight through the doorway into the sink.
Place the bunch of grapes in the bathroom sink.
Turn around and head straight back to the bed, heading to the foot of the bed.
Pick up the grape from the bed.
Head back to the sink.
Place the grape in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two bunches of grapes in a bathroom sink.

high_descs: Walk straight and take a left turn to walk down the passage and take a right turn to enter the bedroom and reach the sidetable.
Pick up a bunch of grape from the nightstand.
Turn around to walk to the sink across the passage on the right.
Put the grape in the sink.
Turn around to walk back to the bedroom and reach the bed.
Pick up the grape on the bed.
Turn around to exit the room and walk across the passage to reach the bathroom sink on the right.
Put the bunch of grapes in the sink next to the other bunch of grapes.
anns.task_desc: Put two bunches of Grape in the Sink.

high_descs: Leave the room. Go straight ahead. Cross to the left when you reach the door. Turn right. Approach the sidetable. Turn left.
Take the grape from the night stand.
Turn around and leave the sink. Turn right. Approach the wall. Turn left. Approach the sink.
Place the grape in the farthest part of the sink.
Turn around and turn right. Move over. Turn left. Enter the room. Turn right, continue to the end of the bed. Turn left, move. Turn left, opposite the bed.
Take the grape.
Leave the sink. Turn left. Reach the entrance to the sink. Turn left.
Place the grape next to the sink.
